statement.p:
Ivana owns two hotels, that earn annual profits of x and y dollars, respectively. She would like her total annual profit from the two hotels to be (exactly) $10,000.






                Fill in the table with some possible values for x and y, in thousands of dollars. (Note that it is possible for one of the hotels to sustain a loss, or negative profit.)




                    x
